      description: "Verify and standardize Dutch customer and business data, including addresses, phone numbers, emails, URLs, VAT, IBAN, Chamber of Commerce (KvK) numbers, and postal codes. Forever free (no auth, https/cors enabled) APIs to check and standardize your data."
      servers: [
